values:
Hellloooooooooo!

It's SaRaH!

Royce and Company got grounded because of their little stunt.

Stupid boys.  hehehehe.


<3

Sarah
Hey I'm Sarah, I changed the layout of Royce's blog just so now it's not dreary and bland.  Dont you just love decorating?  Well talk to you later!

Yo this be Pace. when Royce told me hed be makin a blog I thought he was kidding! So u kno my names pace. I'm 19 years old, an aries, and I enjoy moonlit walks on the beach, playing pong and pranking jordan fox. you should hear bout him soon. :)  actually, mark and royce can wait, I LOVE talkin bout our newest prank!  This is genius, PURE genius.  Shit, here comes drine.

Day 2 at Camp Vamp has just ended!  Oh, Intro: I'm Royce, if you read the Bio you should know that.  I'm posting from Mark's notebook here at Vamp Camp.  It's technically called "Camp Vamp" but it is a "Vamp Camp" so expect me to call it both.  Most everyone arrived today, just the hardcore people arrived yesterday.  Yes I'm in with the crowd.  We were the lucky ducks who got to help set camp up. YAY!!! Well the low-down is there's 3 counselers at this Camp.  There's Jonathan Iso, the son of a bitch who turned me, and I kind of love him for it now, Richard Loft, who's what you might call the "cool" counseler. He really doesn't do anything but cook and chill with us.  Jon makes sure we keep things fun but mellow.  Finally there's James Drine, put simply, he's the dickweed of the group.  HE's had it in for me since my first day here.  Maybe it's cause I blew up his car, killed his dog, and shit on his porch.  I had a bowel problem OK? Don't judge me. 
    I got a pretty tight knit group:  Me, Mark, Sarah, Nikki, Pace and Al.  Pace is my best bud ever, he's had my back since that whole shitting on a faculty porch thing.  Sarah and Nicole came the year after I did, all sweet and innocent, well not any more ; )  Now frankly, they scare me.   Mark's been here the longest out of all of us.  He knows his way around pretty much everything.  Then there's Al.  On Al's first day he stared down Drine.  I can't stare Drine down.  So his SoW (Strength of Will, it's pretty big here at Camp Vamp) was his determining factor.  He REALLY scares me. 
    Along the way I've made a few enemies, but I wont spoil a good entry by talking about them.  You'll be hearing about them soon enough anyways.  

Later!
Royce

P.S. The rest of the gang says hi!
